{"tid":1666810,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港府 / 香港警察公開向清真寺道歉　間接證明武力的重要性？","createTime":"2019-10-21T06:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T07:17:59.000Z","uid":14328,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e040333ee3ec878ddbb6251857d86c908ed8445","tid":1666810,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"香港政府呢４個月嚟，搞到報館記者、耶教教會、學校學生，香港市民<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府／香港警察從不道歉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反之，噴到清真寺，就立即仆出嚟發聲明道歉，連警隊都要仆出嚟幫人抹扶手抹地。<br />\n點解會咁？<br />\n<br />\n怕左全世界伊斯蘭國家＆伊斯蘭教徒？<br />\n<br />\n真係誰大誰惡誰正確？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果香港人可以好似南亞人伊斯蘭教徒咁性格剛烈，手段夠狠，係咪就唔敢恰鳩香港市民？"},{"pid":"e57f42ea53dab1a0849ee26d51e0ccaa8e1132eb","tid":1666810,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"da5c04587c628299380e81ab91a5ea735480db14","tid":1666810,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:42:54.000Z","msg":"屌晒你地<br />\n尋晚開<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動po</span>到而家都仲未上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢單野新鮮滾熱辣 connect全世界<br />\n依家就係最好時機！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地fight for freedom<br />\n我無宗教信仰 但我有宗教自由 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n早喺六月已經有宗教俾popo當眾侮辱 <br />\n打壓宗教自由之餘亦都對各個宗教不尊重<br />\n<br />\n睇原po！<br />\n既然我哋係fight for freedom<br />\n咁我哋更加係時候聲援被打壓宗教自由嘅人！<br />\n快啲一齊討論！<br />\n<br />\n係時候搞個 尊重宗教自由大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665685\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"be5f971aee1f71c4d4440f3107e810a5db188816","tid":1666810,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be6dc8c139ab6c24ce4a1efef92de1abfd5b1be3","t